    "gp_section_552792584305706099": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f690dcc9e1677c8c2dd4a4500ff0059981f3aba7ba2ee7bd05e1edd0870cb578_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-n9gr3-oK_label": "<p>Step 1</p>",
        "gg-vMdwPnao_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e3261c34-ae51-414c-81dd-4e9edf9e512a.png",
        "gg2fynqfSWV_label": "<p>Check Availability Now...</p>",
        "gg2s3Fu3z9K_text": "<p>By gently creating space between your vertebrae, releasing trapped nerves, and improving circulation, <strong>SmoothSpine eliminates the pain at its source, no matter where you feel it.</strong></p>",
        "gg3lLzTDdOS_text": "<p>Designed with Spine Health Specialists and Trusted by Top Sciatic Pain Experts Nationwide</p>",
        "gg3qXa6I1vg_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM will be delivered to your door (ships from our local warehouse within 24 hours on average).</p>",
        "gg4JFz99Gy3_text": "<p><strong><u>TargetPoint Massage Therapy</u></strong> has micro-vibration nodes that mimic the hands of a massage therapist, targeting deep knots and tight muscles to release tension, ease stiffness, and promote circulation for faster results.</p>",
        "gg541QMMpZW_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM is a revolutionary at-home device that <strong>helps you eliminate back pain and Sciatica, reduce inflammation and stiffness, and increase mobility</strong> all without needing invasive surgery or relying on pain pills.</p>",
        "gg5AnEyK174_text": "How Do I Use SmoothSpine TFM?",
        "gg5BgFAsbXG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-771e134f-1096-4615-81eb-fa441a8c71fb.png",
        "gg5hZqy7Vzl_text": "<p>In the unlikely event that you are not satisfied with your purchase, SmoothSpine offers a <strong>90-day money-back guarantee on ALL purchases.</strong></p>",
        "gg6V_sIyQGh_text": "It’s Time to Finally Eliminate Your Back Pain &amp; Sciatica (And Keep It Gone for Good!)",
        "gg6YYGqGoMJ_text": "<p>Simply lay back for 15 minutes a day and let the Triple Fusion Therapy stimulate the natural healing process in your spine - &nbsp;so you can walk, jump, and sleep again without pain holding you back.</p>",
        "gg7eN2QIiHW_text": "<p>Ever since SmoothSpine was released to the public earlier this year, an incredible amount of buzz has been generated. Due to its popularity and overwhelming positive reviews, the company is so confident in their product that they are offering a limited-time discount of up to 60% - this month only.</p>",
        "gg7gtrWtUJ__text": "<p>We’ve worked hard to offer this breakthrough technology at a competitive price, without markups, because <strong>we know how expensive other solutions</strong> are such as surgery, weekly physiotherapy sessions, and the constant cost of pain meds.</p>",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/275d619088e94ed5b4489e52e5f32df3.mp4",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggBzc-BUFzk_text": "Eliminate Sciatic Back Pain: One Breakthrough Device Restores Spinal Discs from Home",
        "ggCR9pMNf_P_text": "With SmoothSpine TFM, getting started is easy:",
        "ggDF1U9uOJJ_text": "Is SmoothSpine TFM Safe?",
        "ggDpxrzwgwj_text": "<p>This completely depends on what pacemaker model you have.</p>",
        "ggEUHj4HmHo_text": "<p>It really is that simple.</p>",
        "ggEh76kowP9_text": "<p>, Ever since <strong>SmoothSpine </strong>was released to the public earlier</p>",
        "ggEq3zcOzTs_text": "How Does SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager Work?",
        "ggFG6AdGk0q_text": "<p><strong>SmoothSpine TFM is designed to alleviate all Sciatica cases, including pain that radiates into your hip, leg, or foot.</strong></p>",
        "ggGw9gxZhIQ_text": "How Fast Can I See Results?",
        "ggHgs612zsq_text": "<p>This means you have 90 days from the time your order arrives at your door to try the product and see how it works for you.</p>",
        "ggIV0LUdnWf_text": "<p>That’s because it targets the root cause—<strong>compressed nerves in the lower spine</strong>—rather than just masking the symptoms like other solutions.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggIsN89vVry_text": "<p>\"Before SmoothSpine, I couldn’t even stand or drive for more than 10 minutes. Now I’m going on walks every morning and even getting back into the gym! <strong>It’s given me my life back.</strong>\"</p>",
        "ggJafmEGs4q_text": "Relieve Back Pain &amp; Sciatica Today!",
        "ggJc2kPVK5Y_label": "<p>Step 3</p>",
        "ggK204xJqMx_text": "<p>It is designed to be used for 15-30 minutes per day and it comes with a plug-in cord making it convenient and easy to use, without ever having to wait to recharge the battery.</p>",
        "ggK3g4lxCnC_text": "<p>~ Earl Horne, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggK7Z8rtqQe_customText": "As Of",
        "ggKOQZwDDdJ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-dc4757cb-4393-4e49-be23-985d6ed82532.png",
        "ggLCedvH6h6_text": "<p><strong>A Special Offer for Our Readers</strong></p>",
        "ggLSHdiIV3P_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM uses Triple Fusion Therapy to <strong>stimulate the natural healing and rehydration process</strong> in damaged or thinned spinal discs allowing users to live pain-free without the need for going under the knife!</p>",
        "ggMF9JucNys_text": "<p>~ Janine Lewis, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1d7401c1caf44072b017951bce82c54a.mp4",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggOeoq5KSo3_text": "What Is the SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager (TFM)?",
        "ggPVHsBMDSV_text": "<p>If you're tired of struggling with chronic back pain, Sciatica, and feeling like a burden on your family, then <u>SmoothSpine TFM is exactly what you need.</u></p>",
        "ggPcNXDSciV_text": "Will SmoothSpine TFM Work for Spinal Stenosis And Herniated Discs?",
        "ggQC5Rx9hMa_text": "<p><strong>SmoothSpine TFM is extremely easy to use. </strong>All you have to do is lay it flat on your bed or floor, position your lower back on top, and press the power button.</p>",
        "ggQHvkrfTNZ_text": "<p>The device features three clinically proven therapies that work together:</p>",
        "ggQxiPyCW7k_label": "<p>Check Availability &gt;&gt;</p>",
        "ggR1WQJD4UZ_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM can only be purchased online at our <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/tfm-pres\"><span style=\"color:#0056B3;\">official website.</span></a></p>",
        "ggRqpnTAU1D_text": "<p>Check availability and take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggS3GePHfon_text": "What If My Pain Is in My Hip or Leg, Not My Back?",
        "ggSLY_ACEPl_text": "<p>If for any reason you are not happy and you have not experienced a complete transformation in your back health, simply reach out to our customer support team at <strong>support@smoohtspine.com</strong>, and they will issue you a <strong>FULL refund—no questions asked.</strong></p>",
        "ggTIWMF6Doa_text": "<p>SmoothSpine will deliver results after the first use, of course, your back will not magically be healed after 1 use however <strong>most users experience a decrease in pain and increase in mobility after just 15-30 minutes.&nbsp;</strong></p>",
        "ggU0SWLogHk_text": "<p>this year, an incredible amount of buzz has been generated. Due to its popularity and overwhelming positive reviews, the company is so confident in their product that they are offering a <strong>limited-time discount of up to 60% - this month only.</strong></p>",
        "ggVEPAomqLy_text": "Can I Use SmoothSpine TFM If I Have a Pacemaker?",
        "ggWJdOpfCQe_text": "Avoid Back Surgery: One Breakthrough Device Restores Spinal Discs from Home",
        "ggZlJRJg2fH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ef8e5b77-645c-42bd-84ee-13b3623df084.png",
        "gg_ci_s3UbB_text": "<p>Enter your shipping and billing information on our secure checkout page, and we will begin to pack your order and send it out the very next day.</p>",
        "gg_fgIh0ti9_text": "<p>\"<strong>My life took a complete 180 after SmoothSpine!</strong> My doctor recommended it to avoid back surgery, and I wish she'd given it to me years ago. <strong>I even got rid of my back brace.</strong> My wife is amazed.”</p>",
        "gg_pY699Tzg_text": "<p><strong><u>Dynamic Traction Therapy</u></strong> gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing pressure on pinched nerves and allowing your spinal discs to rehydrate and regain their natural cushioning.</p>",
        "ggaJ4lx1Jaz_text": "<p>60% discount on this product - only during the launch phase through this link</p>",
        "ggavy2anxq-_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM has gone through thousands of clinical trials and is backed by renowned spine health experts - it has been determined that SmoothSpine TFM is 100% safe for daily use.</p>",
        "ggb_ZMb46rq_text": "<p>SmoothSpine TFM is not available in stores, and please do not fall victim to cheap knockoffs - SmoothSpine TFM is a scientifically designed medical device, and just as you would not take unverified pain medication if you did not know what was in it, you should not use a device that you do not know how or where it was designed</p>",
        "ggbtx4NzI9c_text": "<p>From here, all you have to do is select the traction, heat, and massage setting that is <strong>most comfortable for you.</strong></p>",
        "ggdYXgWfB6X_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-57877a30-b41e-4623-93ca-dd7061d85542.png",
        "ggeBMVuQeJz_label": "<p>Step 2</p>",
        "ggepQZyukxE_text": "Where Can I Purchase SmoothSpine TFM?",
        "ggfEelyLkSE_text": "<p>Our goal is to eliminate all of those costs. Instead, <strong>you just need a one-time payment for SmoothSpine TFM</strong>, which usually retails at $250. However, there is a massive sale until midnight where you can get SmoothSpine TFM for as low as $89 when you select the biggest bundle.</p>",
        "gggkoB4YS-F_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/a1f25f5af9b24b289ab66b3be7f76695.mp4",
        "gggkoB4YS-F_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gggkoB4YS-F_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gghoVeGaVVR_text": "<p>After using SmoothSpine for 14 days, you should experience almost complete relief from daily back pain - you will move easier, walk further, and your whole body should feel decades younger.</p>",
        "ggiIc82ngmW_label": "<p>Step 4</p>",
        "ggixnIcXtIv_text": "Claim Your SmoothSpine TFM Now and Save 60% Until Midnight",
        "ggjYkdFkXhk_label": "<p>Check Discounts &amp; Availability</p>",
        "ggjaqFOYTBo_text": "<p>At SmoothSpine, we are committed to <strong>making long-term pain relief affordable and accessible for anyone who needs it.</strong></p>",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6dfcc0fe62d74444b86a92877407574b.mp4",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggkAgovtx0b_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0b43845d-941c-4b47-b42c-42fe14112ff1.png",
        "ggkQa2qKlTA_customText": "As Of",
        "gglhBQY9Fds_text": "<p>Finally, allow SmoothSpine TFM to turn your stabbing back pain into a feeling of bliss and <strong>relief over the next 15 minutes.</strong></p>",
        "ggn-HrkzObE_text": "<p>Claim Your SmoothSpine TFM Now and <strong>SAVE 60%</strong> UNTIL MIDNIGHT</p>",
        "ggnh0HmgcCI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-29944fd1-d201-4c74-bc68-3464070030ad.png",
        "ggp1rRGlpGy_text": "<p><strong><u>Thermal Circulation Therapy</u></strong> uses heat to boost rehydration and bring healing nutrients to damaged spinal discs.</p>",
        "ggqJoxWzxHh_text": "<p>Click the \"Check Availability\" button below to check if we still have stock (Due to high demand, we sell out fast…).</p>",
        "ggrIon6KC7T_text": "<p>Absolutely. The majority of our customers purchase SmoothSpine TFM because they suffer from spinal stenosis, bulging or herniated discs, or Sciatica and have been told their only option is back surgery.</p>",
        "ggs4PwTGdHp_text": "<p>~ Mario Agosti, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggsu5ob4kWw_text": "What If I Am Not Happy With My Purchase?",
        "ggv-34H59h7_text": "<p>With our <strong>competitive prices, responsive support team, and commitment to your success</strong>, you can trust SmoothSpine to support you on every step of your back pain journey.</p>",
        "ggvfxh-DOVf_text": "How Much Does SmoothSpine Cost?",
        "ggwd-sUAAXx_text": "<p>So if you're ready to turn back the clock on your spine and get back to living without the constant stabbing pain, <strong>click \"Check Availability\" now and let's begin transforming your life today!</strong></p>",
        "ggwjqx_XcKu_text": "<p>\"SmoothSpine is <strong>way cheaper</strong> than all the treatments I’ve tried in the past. My doctor was considering back surgery for me, but now she says <strong>I don’t need it as I’ve realigned my spine.</strong>”</p>",
        "ggxQncbBP47_text": "<p>While SmoothSpine TFM is safe to use with 90% of pacemakers, it’s important that you consult with your doctor before ordering.</p>",
        "ggxUX5yAt3-_text": "<p>If we have stock, you will land on our secure checkout page, where you can choose the bundle that best suits your needs (The bigger the bundle, the more you save).</p>",
        "ggxeiti_fLd_text": "Take advantage of our discount by clicking the link below!",
        "ggyWKKy3GSm_text": "<p>Designed with Spine Health Specialists and Trusted by Leading Nerve Experts Nationwide</p>"
      },
